				<wikidot:authorName>Uncle Nicolini</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3487700</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oa4YdI97-PY">⇢ Recommended listening music ⇠</a></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;⇢&nbsp;Author&nbsp;Thoughts&nbsp;⇠</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I was mostly in charge of cleanup and the dialogue. I wanted to personify this pool as some form of culturally appropriating frat boy who doesn't know his left from his right. Hawaiian (really, Polynesian culture overall tbh) is absolutely beautiful and I did some minor research for this. Expect a Polynesian inspired article from me eventually.</p> <p>Anyway, this was fun to write with my pals. :D</p> </div> </div> </div> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rounderhouse-s-author-page">⇢ More by Rounderhouse ⇠</a><br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/drannoyingdog">⇢ More by DrAnnoyingDog ⇠</a><br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/woedenaz">⇢ More by Woedenaz ⇠</a><br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/uncle-nicolini-author-page">⇢ More by me ⇠</a></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10369980#post-4160565</guid>
				<title>HOW IT BEGAN</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10369980/scp-4512#post-4160565</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 21 Feb 2019 15:58:43 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Woedenaz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404096</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <h2><span>This bad boy is a big, mean, luau party machine!</span></h2> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⇢&nbsp;How&nbsp;this&nbsp;came&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;⇠</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⇣&nbsp;How&nbsp;this&nbsp;came&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;⇣</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/458009355615207424/548171162497318912/Screen_Shot_2019-02-21_at_10.55.52_AM.png" alt="Screen_Shot_2019-02-21_at_10.55.52_AM.png" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> <p>How this actually became a thing can only be explained by the collective insanity of four madmen.</p> <p>Co-written by: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550766387" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" >Woedenaz</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550766387" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550766387" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drannoyingdog" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2425082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550766387" alt="DrAnnoyingDog" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2425082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drannoyingdog" >DrAnnoyingDog</a></span></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⇢&nbsp;Oh&nbsp;hey&nbsp;I&nbsp;like&nbsp;the&nbsp;idea&nbsp;of&nbsp;author&nbsp;thoughts&nbsp;so&nbsp;imma&nbsp;steal&nbsp;it&nbsp;from&nbsp;Nico&nbsp;⇠</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⇣&nbsp;yeet&nbsp;⇣</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>This was literally an idea that popped up out of no where. I was sitting at work and I <em>think</em> I was just kinda mulling over how much I hated cleaning the pool when I was a kid (I grew up in Florida.) And then the image above just sorta happened.</p> <p>Outside of the initial concept, I wrote the containment as well as the containment attempts. Also did a few edits to try and tie each section together.</p> <p>Overall, it's a pretty goofy SCP. It could very easily be a -j if we had wanted to go in that direction. But we wanted to just write something fun, silly, and enjoyable to read. It's probably not for everyone but I hope you enjoy regardless!</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
